"     Seitz WH, Papandrea RF. Fractures and dislocations of the wrist. In: Rockwood and Green's Fractures in Adults, 5th, Bucholz RW, Heckman JD (Eds), Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins, Philadelphia 2002.",
"    </li>",
"   </ol>",
