"      Benekli M, Smiley SL, Younis T, et al, &ldquo;Intensive Conditioning Regimen of Etoposide (VP-16), Cyclophosphamide and Carmustine (VCB) Followed by Autologous Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation for Relapsed and Refractory Hodgkin's Lymphoma,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       Bone Marrow Transplant",
"      </i>",
"      , 2008, 41(7):613-9.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"mobipreview.htm?32/39/33399/abstract-text/18071290/pubmed\" id=\"18071290\" target=\"_blank\">",
"        18071290",
"       </a>",
"       ]",
"      </span>",
"     </div>",
"    </li>",
